Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:32.28,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}If I become normal, can I stay close?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:37.77,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}With the children, we link our arms
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:42.90,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}Make a circle and sing a song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:49.66,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}Knowing there was no chair for me all along
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:52.68,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}You locked me into the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.83,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}I’m your preserved flower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:58.51,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}The world is too slow to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:00.59,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}Not all blossoms spark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:02.26,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}And spikes may be sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:06.73,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}They want to see just the beautiful parts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:10.12,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}Sitting in a shower of scarlet rain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:12.38,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}It all used to be ours
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:14.54,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}I’m counting the hours
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:17.86,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}Hours that stood between us like a river
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.89,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}Once I crawled through the water
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:25.59,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}All I ever knew have become distant past
